data.title: Distance from Panipat to Kairana
data.meta_description: Distance from Pānīpat to Kairāna how many miles and kilometers, how far is it from Panipat to Kairana travel distance.
data.text:
The air travel (bird fly) shortest distance between Pānīpat and Kairāna is 23 km= 14 miles.

If you travel with an airplane (which has average speed of 560 miles) from Panipat to Kairana, It takes 0.03 hours to arrive.
